        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-6">

            <h5 class="font-weight-bold mb-5">Action Bar - Layout and Rules</h5>

            <p>The action bar is meant to house any and  all information related to the resort or cabins.  On desktop it should span the length of the browser, on mobile it will be housed within  an expand/collapse state.</p>

            <p>For Dollywood, we have included the following: </p>
            
            <p><strong>Select Lodging:</strong> this dropdown serves to include the Resort, Cabins, Packages or Off-Site Hotels.</p>
            
            <p><strong>How Many?:</strong> this dropdown allows for selection of the number of guests and their age range from adult or senior.</p>
            
            <p><strong>When?:</strong> this dropdown houses a calendar that allows the user to select when & how many days.
            </p>

            </div>
